<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains what personal data we collect and how we use it.</p>
<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Information that identifies you.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information on how the service is accessed and used.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>To Provide and Maintain the Service:</strong> Ensure the service is running smoothly.</li>
    <li><strong>To Notify You About Changes:</strong> Inform you about modifications to our services.</li>
    <li><strong>To Provide Customer Support:</strong> Assist you with any issues you encounter.</li>
    <li><strong>To Gather Analysis for Improvement:</strong> Understand how to improve our services.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>We use commercially acceptable methods to protect your personal data, but no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

<h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.</p>

